Additional details


Discover the Fitbit Versa 4 Fitness smartwatch designed for those who prioritize health, precision, and seamless connectivity in their active lifestyles. This versatile device offers comprehensive health tracking with its advanced sensors, including a multi-path optical heart rate sensor and red and infrared sensors for blood oxygen saturation (SpO2) monitoring. These features allow you to stay informed about your heart health and overall wellness. The skin temperature sensor, available through the Fitbit app, adds another layer of insight, helping you understand changes in your body's baseline. The Fitbit Versa 4 for men and women features over 40+ exercise modes that automatically track your every move, ensuring you stay on top of your fitness goals. Whether you're running, biking, or practicing yoga, the built-in GPS and GLONASS deliver accurate pace and distance metrics without needing your phone. The Cardio Fitness Score offers a comprehensive view of your cardiovascular health, making it easier to track progress and optimize workouts. Plus, with water resistance up to 50 meters, it's ready for any aquatic adventure. Stay connected with on-wrist Bluetooth calls, text notifications, and app alerts, even when your phone is out of reach. The Versa 4's integration with Alexa allows for easy control of smart home devices and access to information on the go. Navigate your day effortlessly with Google Maps and make secure transactions with Google Wallet directly from your wrist. With a battery life of over 6 days and fast charging capability. Designed for comfort and style, Compatible with both iOS and Android devices, the Versa 4 smart watch offers a seamless experience, making it the perfect companion for those who value both technology and aesthetics.
